Arnaud, I'm pretty sure that you have a wheel cylinder issue on the front
driver's side. It might be an air bubble, it might be grease on the brakes,
or it might be a leaking/faulty wheel cylinder.
Check those out! Be careful driving out there!!
Let us know what you find.

